text: Koror is the former capital city of Palau. Palau is divided into sixteen states, and Koror is one of the states in Palau. The state of Koror has about 90% of the population of the country. Koror is also the largest town, with a population of 14,000 (2004). Category:Capital cities in Oceania Category:Settlements in Palau
title: Koror City
